stories.title: Shaun Pollock fined 100 per cent of match fee for dissent, Boucher cleared
stories.summary: South Africa's Shaun Pollock has been fined 100 per cent of his match fee after being found guilty of dissent while team-mate Mark Boucher was cleared of using obscene language in the third One Day International match between Pakistan and South

stories.title: Kallis and Smith lead South African run-chase
stories.subTitle: Pakistan v South Africa, 3rd ODI, Faisalabad
